make sure other tanks do not attack until assist is called.<br>
make sure other tanks stand back until called in.<br>
<br>
work on establishing your MT with gear to help him maintain aggro.<br>
<br>
while it is nice to kill mobs with very few people, it's even nicer to get the kill.  <br>
